I have successfully compared the travel times between car and bicycle routes from Lower Manhattan to Upper Manhattan:
- Car route: 9.9km, 17 minutes
- Bicycle route: 9.4km, 42 minutes

The bicycle route is slightly shorter in distance (0.5km less), but takes significantly longer (25 minutes more) than the car route. This completes the task of comparing travel times between the two transportation modes. I'll send a summary message to the user.
